title: WWU’s College of Business and Economics to Host Jeffrey Hollender Nov. 30 (Western Washington University) ...
text: ( Source : Western Washington University ) Western Washington University's College of Business and Economics ( CBE ) will host Jeffrey Hollender as part of its Sustainability Speaker Series from 1:45-2:45 p.m. on Friday Nov. 13 in Parks Hall 441
